WEBVTT

00:02.988 --> 00:04.522
Look, I know that
you have spent your life

00:04.623 --> 00:06.323
taking care of other people.

00:06.391 --> 00:08.759
Now I am gonna take care of you,
Norma Bates.

00:08.827 --> 00:10.693
Look, I really like your mom.

00:10.762 --> 00:16.400
She's a good woman,
and I care for her.

00:16.501 --> 00:18.269
- This is all Dylan's fault.
- Don't blame him, mom.

00:18.370 --> 00:19.870
He's just worried about me!

00:19.938 --> 00:21.405
No, he's just trying
to turn you against me!

00:21.473 --> 00:22.394
No one could do that!

00:22.403 --> 00:24.083
These girls were brought here
from China.

00:24.201 --> 00:28.112
Then guys came to the motel
to try them out.

00:28.213 --> 00:29.914
So, you know the girl from
the manga book, right?

00:30.015 --> 00:32.049
- Of course.
- Help me.

00:32.116 --> 00:35.052
I found her.

00:35.120 --> 00:37.120
She was being held prisoner
in Shelby's basement.

00:37.189 --> 00:38.956
I think he was running
some kind of Asian sex slave

00:39.057 --> 00:40.791
business with Keith Summers.

00:40.859 --> 00:44.261
Sometimes you hear and see
things that aren't there.

00:44.329 --> 00:47.965
- That's not true.
- It's true.

00:48.066 --> 00:50.100
This is the girl.
The girl I told you about.

00:50.202 --> 00:52.636
The girl from the basement.
Tell her!

00:52.704 --> 00:56.640
Tell her you were locked
in that cop's basement.

00:56.708 --> 01:00.544
This is not the man, right?

01:00.612 --> 01:02.613
He is the man.

